OL,5,Cjudge rules
OL,7,FIt was reported to the panel that on
OL,8,F20 April of that year he met the PCSO,
OL,9,Fwho was off duty, and had sex with her
OL,10,Fon a sofa.
OL,12,FThe officer, based in Cheadle, then
OL,13,Fended the relationship.
OL,15,FIn the report to the panel it was said
OL,16,Fhe "failed to act with self-control or
OL,17,Fprofessionalism in pursuing an
OL,18,Finappropriate relationship with a
OL,19,Fsubordinate colleague".
