OL,5,Cjudge rules
OL,7,FHe also "failed to live up to the
OL,8,Fleadership and managerial
OL,9,Fresponsibilities expected" and created
OL,10,Fa "toxic working environment for
OL,11,Fjunior colleagues that was only
OL,12,Faddressed when a junior colleague
OL,13,Freported the issue", the report said.
OL,15,FIn November last year, the panel
OL,16,Fimposed a final written warning.
OL,18,FGreater Manchester Police challenged
OL,19,Fthe panel's decision, arguing at the
OL,20,FHigh Court in London that Mr Taylor
OL,21,Fshould have been dismissed.
