OL,5,Cjudge rules
OL,7,FBut Mr Justice Swift dismissed the
OL,8,Fclaim, describing the panel's decision
OL,9,Fas "sufficiently reasoned" in a
OL,10,Fjudgment on Monday.
OL,12,FHe said the panel considered
OL,13,Fpsychiatric evidence that Mr Taylor's
OL,14,Fdecision-making was impaired because
OL,15,Fof mental health issues.
OL,17,FHe also said he did not believe the
OL,18,Fpanel's decision to be irrational and
OL,19,Fthat it had "carefully assessed the
OL,20,Fseriousness of the misconduct".
